      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Mincho Georgiev</b>\n</p><p><b>Mincho Georgiev</b>,<br />\na Bulgarian computer chess programmer and author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Pawny\" title=\"Pawny\">Pawny</a>, \nfirst released in September 2009 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mincho_Georgiev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mincho_Georgiev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=29480\">Alqrainys Hash Function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 21, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=29641&amp;start=9\">Re: New open source engine called \"Pawny\"</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 04, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29763\">Pawny - new version (0.11)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 2009</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mincho_Georgiev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=340114\">Re: Null-move pruning and the hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 31, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=341576\">Question for Nalimov experts</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 10, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Nalimov_Tablebases\" title=\"Nalimov Tablebases\">Nalimov Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-chess.org/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=408\">Small optimization question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">OpenChess Forum</a>, July 08, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=40229\">On history counters again</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 31, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44599\">QSearch, checks and the lack of progress...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2012 &#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mincho_Georgiev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=60531\">Android Request</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 19, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Android\" title=\"Android\">Android</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59691&amp;start=22\">Re: Some questions from a beginner</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Mincho Georgiev</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>,  April 06, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Looking_for_Magics\" title=\"Looking for Magics\">Looking for Magics</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mincho_Georgiev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20090908151549/http://pawny.netii.net:80/\">Pawny's Homepage</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, September 08, 2009)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190805192504/http://pawny.netii.net/\">Pawny's Homepage</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, August 05, 2019)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mincho_Georgiev&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29641\">New open source engine called \"Pawny\"</a> by <a href=\"/Graham_Banks\" title=\"Graham Banks\">Graham Banks</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 2009</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nN